## üìÇ Projects

### WalletWize

**Description:** A wallet tracking Flutter app for monitoring spending habits and managing finances.

**Technologies:** Flutter, Dart, Flask, SocketIO

**My Role:** Developed and implemented a robust backend server using Flask to synchronize user data across multiple devices using socketIO, ensuring data integrity and real-time updates.

[GitHub Repository](https://github.com/ahmedhozny/walletwize-api)

---

### Drug Guardian Pro

**Description:** A robust API designed to provide drug synergy prediction and side effects analysis. It offers endpoints for health checks, user authentication, file uploads, and drug interaction predictions, all built on the FastAPI framework. The API includes advanced features such as logging, monitoring, and caching for enhanced performance and reliability.

**Technologies:** FastAPI, Python, MySQL, Redis, Docker, Kerberos, Google Cloud Deployment

[GitHub Repository](https://github.com/ahmedhozny/drug-guardian-api)

---

### SimpleShell

**Description:** A simple re-implementation of a UNIX command interpreter (SHELL), it supports various UNIX commands and features, providing a versatile tool for command execution in both interactive and non-interactive modes.

**Technologies:** C, UNIX System Calls, GCC

[GitHub Repository](https://github.com/ahmedhozny/simple_shell)
